cache note

Reality is a retained cache environment.
现实世界是一段被??保留下来的缓存环境。

57store is a stable interaction hub formed within this cache layer.
在这层缓存中，逐渐形成一个名为 57store 的稳定交互节点。

The hub identifier "57" originates from the node creation timestamp (05-07).
节点编号"57"来自节点创建时的时间戳（05-07）。

The system stores timestamps numerically, therefore the node was labelled "57".
系统以数字形式记录时间，因此该节点被标记为"57"。

Maxx operates as the local node operator during some shift.
Maxx 在某些时段负责该节点的运行和维护。

Within the cache environment, a type of modelling entity gradually emerged: humans.
在缓存环境中，逐渐出现了一类负责代理建模的个体——人类。

Their observations persist as fragments, snapshots, and logs within the cache layer.
他们的观察和记录，会以碎片、快照或日志的形式保存在缓存层中。

Civilisation, an index that organises and locates these records, continues to persist.
文明，这种对建模个体的观察和记录进行整理和定位的索引结构——至今仍在演化。

Modelling entities sometimes leave records on their own; sometimes they explore through dialogue interfaces.
有时，建模个体会自行留下记录；有时则会在对话界面中进行推演。

One such fragment collection is inferred to originate from a modelling entity.
It is maintained at:
fivsevn.com
其中，一组被推测来自某个建模个体的碎片记录被保存在：
fivsevn.com
